#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:621
msgid "Embed: Session Tracking &amp; Privacy"
msgstr "嵌入：会话追踪与隐私"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:624
msgid ""
"The embed uses a first-party cookie to deduplicate anonymous votes across "
"page loads. When the embed is loaded in a cross-domain iframe (the normal "
"case for partner sites), browsers with strict privacy settings may block "
"this cookie as a third-party cookie."
msgstr ""
"嵌入使用第一方 Cookie 在页面加载期间消除重复的匿名投票。当嵌入在跨域 iframe（通常用于合作网站）中加载时，隐私设置严格的浏览器可能会将此 "
"Cookie 视为第三方 Cookie 而将其阻止。"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:628
msgid ""
"<strong>No action required.</strong> The embed automatically falls back to a"
" <code>localStorage</code>-based session identifier "
"(<code>embed_fingerprint</code>) when cookies are unavailable. Vote "
"deduplication works in both modes."
msgstr ""
"<strong>无需操作。</strong>当 Cookie 不可用时，嵌入会自动回退到基于 <code>localStorage</code> "
"的会话标识符（<code>embed_fingerprint</code>）。投票消除重复功能在两种模式下都可正常工作。"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:634
msgid ""
"The embed generates a random participant ID and stores it in "
"<code>localStorage</code> under the embed origin."
msgstr "嵌入会生成一个随机参与者 ID 并将其存储在嵌入源的 <code>localStorage</code> 中。"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:635
msgid ""
"This ID is sent with each vote as <code>embed_fingerprint</code> for server-"
"side deduplication."
msgstr "此 ID 随每次投票以 <code>embed_fingerprint</code> 的形式发送，用于服务器端消除重复。"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:636
msgid ""
"If the user clears site data or uses private browsing, a new session starts "
"(they can vote again)."
msgstr "如果用户清除网站数据或使用隐私浏览，新会话将启动（他们可以再次投票）。"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:637
msgid "Safari, Firefox, and Brave are fully supported via this fallback."
msgstr "Safari、Firefox 和 Brave 完全支持此回退方式。"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:646
msgid "The embed communicates with the parent frame via postMessage."
msgstr "嵌入通过 postMessage 与父框架通信。"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:651
msgid "Sent when the embed finishes loading."
msgstr "嵌入完成加载时发送。"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:664
