msgstr "立即复制并存储此密钥。出于安全考虑，它将不会再次显示。"

#: app/templates/partner/portal/dashboard.html:26
msgid "Your new webhook signing secret (shown once)"
msgstr "您的新 webhook 签名密钥（仅显示一次）"

#: app/templates/partner/portal/dashboard.html:31
